---
title: Speedy Honey Garlic Beef Fried Rice with Sweetcorn and Green Beans
description: Inspired by a popular takeaway favourite, this Speedy Honey Garlic Beef Fried Rice is ready in just 25 minutes. Layers of flavour with Indonesian style spices, honey and spicy sambal make this easy dish full of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R14_W44_UK_QF11039-15_Main__3low-e33144e4.jpg
